Codehesion is South Africa’s premier mobile app development company, and the perfect place for developers to take their career to the next level. Codehesion has experienced huge growth over the past 12 months and is expanding its team to meet the strong demand for its services. If you are a front-end developer or back-end developer, Codehesion has opportunities available in Gauteng, Cape Town, and Durban. Great news is that if you apply within the month of June and are successfully recruited, you will get a recruitment bonus paid to you. Codehesion prides itself on offering a great work environment and providing its developers with the opportunity to work on “greenfield” projects. Its head office is based in Gauteng, and its new hybrid offices are set to open in Cape Town and Durban this year. Wherever you work from, however, you will be part of a close-knit team that takes on exciting challenges. This includes working on new projects and having a big impact on the finished product. For new developers, Codehesion gives you the chance to learn how to make the best Android and iOS apps on the market. For experienced developers, Codehesion allows you to move away from only working on legacy code or making small changes on huge, established systems. Level up your developer career today – click here to apply to work at Codehesion.